<p>

My experience in that team is what motivated me to move into a leadership role.

I wanted to create a better working environment for designers and for everyone else working in Digital teams in Defra.

And I also wanted to establish and grow the understanding of design across the organisation.

</p>


    <figure>
    <div class="third">
      <img src="/images/posts/leadership-in-context/four.jpg" loading="lazy" alt="the-possibilities-with-patterns - slide two">
